1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:24,219
[SPEAKER_01] Najvažnje, da sad usutno, odkryva, bože, šta s tih tijom, katsme vtijom, katsme zanje, šta s samom pamirom, takže, zanje katsme vržavu, da to už poedem i o tom srykom,

2
00:00:24,219 --> 00:00:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] Prijedoslovci znaju dobro, da u šunji nema dva lista jednaka, a povijete ko kada štuma, će vam što je sasno, nema dva lista jednaka,

3
00:00:39,539 --> 00:00:47,439
[SPEAKER_01] toliko je po ovog srednoća da se razigralo u tom stvaranju, a što mislite te izlodima?

4
00:00:49,359 --> 00:00:58,679
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, priroda je mrtva, mi se nema duši, čovjek ima, i sada je pitanje,

5
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:07,819
[SPEAKER_01] ta srednoć Božja, koja se razigrala u stvaranju čovjeka, stvora ime,

6
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] i dala me u tom reme, u taj prostor, i nismo mi slučajni od svojih oditelja, nismo mi slučajni u ovom ambijentu.

7
00:01:20,260 --> 00:01:22,280
[SPEAKER_01] To je Boži plan.

8
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:28,959
[SPEAKER_01] E sad moram otkriti, kako da ja ostvarim taj Boži plan?

9
00:01:29,799 --> 00:01:36,379
[SPEAKER_01] Vi svi znate, iz Biblije, Bog služi čovjeka na svoju sviku.

10
00:01:36,379 --> 00:01:40,060
[SPEAKER_01] Sviku i priroku.

11
00:01:40,060 --> 00:01:42,299
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo Božja svika.

12
00:01:42,299 --> 00:01:48,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, upravo da to štisku slobodna mi ječe.

13
00:01:48,099 --> 00:01:54,799
[SPEAKER_01] U nas mi je stvori odno, kakava para, koja je mehanočki jav.

14
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:58,920
[SPEAKER_01] da, nego dao nam je razum, srce.

15
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:02,560
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek ima tri posebna.

16
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ima duch, duša i tijelo.

17
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:12,759
[SPEAKER_01] Na tijelu i na dušu džavao može oticati, na duch ne može.

18
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] On samo može oticati na naš osjećaj, na naši tijelu, a na duch ne može.

19
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:29,419
[SPEAKER_01] I sada, kako poredati heraklju bilenota u svog života?

20
00:02:29,419 --> 00:02:32,740
[SPEAKER_01] Što je na prvom mjestu?

21
00:02:32,740 --> 00:02:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] Jasno?

22
00:02:34,699 --> 00:02:38,020
[SPEAKER_01] Na prvom mjestu na pročine smo najsličniji Boga.

23
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:39,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je taj duh.

24
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] Duh koji, na prvom mjestu, da možemo slobodno živjeti.

25
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:52,039
[SPEAKER_01] Jer upravo po to svobodu, čovjek može bijati.

26
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] Jer da nemam slobode, bilju bi robote.

27
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je veliki problem.

28
00:02:59,199 --> 00:03:05,199
[SPEAKER_01] Kod formacije, problem je osvojiti slobodu.

29
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:10,439
[SPEAKER_01] Oslobodu da ne budemo navecani.

30
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne budemo robovi.

31
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] To je uspjeh, osloboda.

32
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:21,379
[SPEAKER_01] Ako netko želi stvarno rasti u formaciji,

33
00:03:21,379 --> 00:03:27,439
[SPEAKER_01] mora raditi puno na tome, da osvoji nutarnu slobodu.

34
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:31,259
[SPEAKER_01] Da nista me ne zarobljava.

35
00:03:31,259 --> 00:03:34,860
[SPEAKER_01] Da nisem na što nisam vežan.

36
00:03:34,860 --> 00:03:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] Često puta, kad razgovaram s hladima,

37
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,740
[SPEAKER_01] oni mi znaju reći,

38
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,620
[SPEAKER_01] znači, ja sam odlučio.

39
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:45,340
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja nika gledam,

40
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:47,319
[SPEAKER_01] ako stari luk,

41
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:49,419
[SPEAKER_01] odgojite da na vidim,

42
00:03:49,419 --> 00:03:51,900
[SPEAKER_01] sinko, nisti je odlučio,

43
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:54,639
[SPEAKER_01] ti si samo palao tam gdje se nadio.

44
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, odlučiti.

45
00:03:58,539 --> 00:04:01,319
[SPEAKER_01] Može samo porusiti svoboda mi je veza.

46
00:04:01,319 --> 00:04:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] Obuta dolazi iz prosučivanja vrednota.

47
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:11,080
[SPEAKER_01] I zna bi ja mogu dao stvarno donositi zdrave obuke.

48
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mora biti čovjek koji uspije osvoboditi se,

49
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,319
[SPEAKER_01] ne navezati se.

50
00:04:20,019 --> 00:04:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo danas, djeca ovo vremena,

51
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:27,379
[SPEAKER_01] koja postaju roboj sredstava.

52
00:04:27,379 --> 00:04:32,120
[SPEAKER_01] Pa su sredstvoje, dakle, nešto što nam služimo.

53
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:36,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako to sredstvo postaje gospodaroč,

54
00:04:36,259 --> 00:04:39,240
[SPEAKER_01] onda ja rušim svoje dostojanstvo.

55
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:44,040
[SPEAKER_01] I to je veliki problem kod formacije.

56
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:48,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ako čovjek postaje roboj sredstava,

57
00:04:49,139 --> 00:04:50,439
[SPEAKER_01] onda nije slova.

58
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:52,339
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je naveljena.

59
00:04:52,339 --> 00:04:54,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pjesnik rekao,

60
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] kod god koracam,

61
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,639
[SPEAKER_01] hoću da bacam

62
00:04:58,639 --> 00:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] snopove zlatne svijetosti.

63
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] ma neću da moji dani proloži u zalude.

64
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:10,100
[SPEAKER_01] To je zapravo prevažno odviti vrijednost vremena

65
00:05:10,100 --> 00:05:15,680
[SPEAKER_01] i sposobnost svoje svobode i odušivanja i objeljenja.

66
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:19,240
[SPEAKER_01] onda se ja sad proložišao vrijednim.

67
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,839
[SPEAKER_01] Na moja vrijednost.

68
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:25,279
[SPEAKER_01] Nije onda od toga što sam ja nešto postigao.

69
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:28,519
[SPEAKER_01] Vrijednost je od toga što mi je Bog poklonio.

70
00:05:28,980 --> 00:05:32,279
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo poklonio mi je tu vrijednost

71
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] da me učinio Djetretom Božim.

72
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:37,279
[SPEAKER_01] Pokrštejno.

73
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je dostojanstvo

74
00:05:40,579 --> 00:05:42,779
[SPEAKER_01] najmogovečej naloženje.

75
00:05:42,779 --> 00:05:45,879
[SPEAKER_01] Biti Djetem Božim.

76
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,579
[SPEAKER_01] To znači

77
00:05:47,579 --> 00:05:50,680
[SPEAKER_01] byti tako familialem s Bohom,

78
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] kao objete Božim.

79
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:56,480
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je moje dostojanstvo.

80
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ja kao objete Božim,

81
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] otrjem,

82
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:01,480
[SPEAKER_01] kako da ja

83
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,980
[SPEAKER_01] istinski učení,

84
00:06:03,980 --> 00:06:07,180
[SPEAKER_01] da Božia bude na prvojom městu.

85
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] Znate,

86
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:11,980
[SPEAKER_01] kada obilazim za krizme,

87
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:13,980
[SPEAKER_01] obično se susjećam

88
00:06:13,980 --> 00:06:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] sa krizmenicima

89
00:06:15,980 --> 00:06:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] i onda postavljam mi pitanja

90
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] i oni meni postavljaju pitanje.

91
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] I onda mi pita

92
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:24,980
[SPEAKER_01] jedna djevojka,

93
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] tada je baš bio

94
00:06:25,980 --> 00:06:27,980
[SPEAKER_01] pitanjem pravršenja blaženja

95
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ivana Merca,

96
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,480
[SPEAKER_01] pa se o tom kono govorilo,

97
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] kako je manka,

98
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,480
[SPEAKER_01] kako su svega.

99
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] I onda ona mene pita,

100
00:06:37,180 --> 00:06:39,680
[SPEAKER_01] da mi možemo postati svetice.

101
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,680
[SPEAKER_01] Nećemo da možemo,

102
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,680
[SPEAKER_01] nego smo poznani.

103
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,680
[SPEAKER_01] Svi smo mi poznani biti svetice.

104
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:49,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ona nadu bude na prvom mjestu.

105
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:53,680
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno ideš putem svetosti.

106
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:56,680
[SPEAKER_01] E tu je naša najveća gorba.

107
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,180
[UNKNOWN] kako?

108
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] Da nam Božja

109
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:03,180
[SPEAKER_01] ide na prvom mjestu.

110
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] Tad ćemo mi

111
00:07:05,180 --> 00:07:07,180
[SPEAKER_01] imati svoje pravo mjesto.

112
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:10,680
[SPEAKER_01] jer kad budi kod na kod na mjesto,

113
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,680
[SPEAKER_01] tada se čovjek uruša.

114
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:16,680
[SPEAKER_01] I prva što je u svom životu

115
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:17,680
[SPEAKER_01] naći

116
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] da Božja pute na prvom mjeru.

117
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] da ja sam kao čovjek vijedan.

118
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:25,180
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sudatelji je od Bogu.

119
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:27,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih prečela samo na način.

120
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:29,180
[SPEAKER_01] Posto mi je to izazor

121
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:31,180
[SPEAKER_01] da vi razmišljate.

122
00:07:32,180 --> 00:07:34,180
[SPEAKER_01] Niste slučajno na ovom svijetu.

123
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:36,180
[SPEAKER_01] Niste bezvinni.

124
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:38,680
[SPEAKER_01] Bož sama ozbiljava čovjek.

125
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:41,180
[SPEAKER_01] Kako?

126
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,180
[SPEAKER_01] No način.

127
00:07:42,180 --> 00:07:43,180
[SPEAKER_01] Taj način

128
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:44,680
[SPEAKER_01] sudatelji Bogu

129
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:47,680
[SPEAKER_01] da se ja u životu ostavim.

130
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:50,680
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nema u životu gore

131
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:54,680
[SPEAKER_01] osjećaja kao promašan život.

132
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:57,680
[SPEAKER_01] I završava će vam priča.

133
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,680
[SPEAKER_01] Kažu tega istočni.

134
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,180
[SPEAKER_01] Završava.

135
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:04,180
[SPEAKER_01] Viđtao soje.

136
00:08:04,180 --> 00:08:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] Sjuramike.

137
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:08,180
[SPEAKER_01] Što je najmora u životu?

138
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:11,180
[SPEAKER_01] Onda šo doshku razzi.

139
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:12,180
[SPEAKER_01] Rekli.

140
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] Najmora u životu.

141
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:16,680
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj se razvulis.

142
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,180
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ši teža.

143
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:19,180
[SPEAKER_01] Še bitrogiva.

144
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] Završi malzami si.

145
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:24,180
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj nije.

146
00:08:24,180 --> 00:08:26,180
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj sam biopoša.

147
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:27,180
[SPEAKER_01] Tak sam vidio.

148
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:28,180
[SPEAKER_01] Koma evovi.

149
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,180
[SPEAKER_01] Da se prepustamo ko me vole.

150
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:33,179
[SPEAKER_01] To nije najbolji.

151
00:08:33,179 --> 00:08:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] Onda dođe drugi mudraci.

152
00:08:35,179 --> 00:08:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj bi carer.

153
00:08:36,179 --> 00:08:38,179
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolji u životu ostaviti.

154
00:08:38,179 --> 00:08:40,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa po matušiš.

155
00:08:40,179 --> 00:08:43,179
[SPEAKER_01] On zamisli se.

156
00:08:43,179 --> 00:08:44,179
[SPEAKER_01] Nije.

157
00:08:44,179 --> 00:08:45,179
[SPEAKER_01] Da mog stavlja čače.

158
00:08:45,179 --> 00:08:46,179
[SPEAKER_01] Nije.

159
00:08:46,179 --> 00:08:48,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bi ja sam upeljati kraju.

160
00:08:48,179 --> 00:08:50,179
[SPEAKER_01] Starci se muri.

161
00:08:50,179 --> 00:08:54,179
[SPEAKER_01] Onda tek treći dođe.

162
00:08:54,679 --> 00:08:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] Cari carer.

163
00:08:56,179 --> 00:08:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] Najbolji u životu probašni život.

164
00:08:59,179 --> 00:09:03,179
[SPEAKER_01] Živjeti u praznu.

165
00:09:03,179 --> 00:09:06,179
[SPEAKER_01] To je najbolji.

166
00:09:06,179 --> 00:09:09,179
[SPEAKER_01] Živjeti da se ostaviti.

167
00:09:09,179 --> 00:09:13,179
[SPEAKER_01] A ostaviti se ako znam s Bogom služiti.

168
00:09:14,179 --> 00:09:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] Evo.

169
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] Sad da bi ja.

170
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ove svoje misli.

171
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] Završio.

172
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:20,679
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mogo bi dobro naći.

173
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:22,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bi sada ostavio.

174
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:23,679
[UNKNOWN] Mogućnost.

175
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:26,679
[UNKNOWN] Da li možda postaviti kakvo pitanje.

176
00:09:26,679 --> 00:09:27,179
[UNKNOWN] Jasno.

177
00:09:27,179 --> 00:09:28,179
[UNKNOWN] Ako ja štažim.

178
00:09:28,179 --> 00:09:29,179
[UNKNOWN] Vrlo rado ću.

179
00:09:29,179 --> 00:09:34,179
[UNKNOWN] Ja ću pobiti leto.

180
00:09:34,179 --> 00:09:35,179
[UNKNOWN] Sve malo bravre.

181
00:09:35,179 --> 00:09:37,179
[UNKNOWN] Poznato je da ste bili bili.

182
00:09:37,179 --> 00:09:39,179
[UNKNOWN] A to će li možda njih interesirati.

183
00:09:39,179 --> 00:09:41,179
[SPEAKER_00] Na dva ispora za papu.

184
00:09:41,179 --> 00:09:42,179
[SPEAKER_00] Papu Benedita XVI.

185
00:09:42,179 --> 00:09:44,179
[SPEAKER_00] I Papu Franja.

186
00:09:44,179 --> 00:09:45,179
[SPEAKER_00] A kak te dobira papu.

187
00:09:45,179 --> 00:09:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] Vreći vam na taj način.

188
00:09:46,179 --> 00:09:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle.

189
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:48,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ja možda vam ispričati da to gira.

190
00:09:48,179 --> 00:09:51,179
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo rado ću ispričati.

191
00:09:51,179 --> 00:09:52,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam.

192
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:54,179
[SPEAKER_01] Zaista je moj milost.

193
00:09:54,179 --> 00:09:56,679
[SPEAKER_01] Valkuta biti u gomplavama.

194
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:59,679
[SPEAKER_01] Probat ću kratko.

195
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je to dosta drug pročit.

196
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:03,179
[SPEAKER_01] Prvo.

197
00:10:03,179 --> 00:10:04,679
[UNKNOWN] Kad jedan papu.

198
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:05,679
[UNKNOWN] Vreć.

199
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,679
[UNKNOWN] Ili pao što je od 2016.

200
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:08,679
[UNKNOWN] Gosto izbio.

201
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:12,679
[SPEAKER_01] Onda se sa zovu svi kardinali.

202
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:15,679
